snippet.title: Underfell: One Hell of a Show | Full Battles | All Endings
snippet.description:
An Underfell Fan-Game containing multiple battles! Fight against Mettaton, the killer robot with a penchant for stardom, who hopes to finally become popular with his most daring act yet: killing a human!

This took me 6 hours to record everything so I hope you enjoy!

This video got copyrighted so I just muted it. As you can imagine I'm not a big fan of having a copyrighted video over my head.

↓ Download Underfell One Hell of a Show! Here ↓
https://gamejolt.com/games/Underfell-Mettaton/853341
